---
title: HelloHero: Smooth Dory & Lemon Butter with Zesty Potato Chunks & Herby Mayo
description: Tender pan-seared fish never fails to satisfy! It has all the familiar tastes of home cooking at its finest, plus a buttery lemon sauce and a side of easy roast potatoes which make up the perfect accompaniments to this tasty dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
